--Dinobots, Thunderwing--

The six Maximals where walking through the woods talking when
Grimlock 
saw the three Destrocons unite.

Grimlock calls out to the other Dinobots, "Dinobots attack the 
Predacons before they can attack those helpless Maximals."

The six Maximals stood behind the three Predacons pointing their guns 
toward them.

--Grimlock--
"Predacons put down your weapons." He says toward the three Predacons.
